---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FILE 003 — NOTES FROM THE CELLS">
  <div id="gate-wrapper">

    <!-- Access denied -->
    <div id="access-denied" class="min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4">
      <div class="border border-p-red/50 bg-p-panel p-10 text-center max-w-md shadow-red-glow">
        <div class="text-p-red text-5xl font-display mb-4">⊗</div>
        <h1 class="font-display text-xl tracking-widest text-p-red mb-4">ACCESS DENIED</h1>
        <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-sm mb-6">
          INMATE PROFILE NOT ON FILE.<br/>
          COMPLETE INTAKE PROCESSING TO CONTINUE.
        </p>
        <a href="/avatar" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 border border-p-teal text-p-teal font-display text-xs tracking-widest hover:bg-p-teal/10 transition-all">
          GO TO INTAKE →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Access granted -->
    <div id="access-granted" class="hidden">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">

        <!-- Back link -->
        <a href="/unlocked" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-ui text-p-unlock/60 text-xs tracking-widest hover:text-p-unlock transition-all mb-8">
          ← CLASSIFIED FILES
        </a>

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="mb-12 border-b border-p-unlock/30 pb-8">
          <p class="font-ui text-p-unlock text-xs tracking-[0.4em] mb-2">FILE 003</p>
          <h1 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-wide text-p-text">NOTES FROM THE CELLS</h1>
          <p class="font-body text-p-dim text-sm mt-2">Panopticon: ACT 1 — ISSUE 1</p>
          <div class="w-16 h-px bg-p-unlock mt-4"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Script content -->
        <div class="script-content space-y-12">

          <!-- PAGE 1 -->
          <div class="border-l-2 border-p-accent/30 pl-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-sm tracking-widest text-p-accent mb-6">PAGE 1 — PANOPTICON PRISON</h3>

            <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-p-text text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 1</p>
                <p>High up near the ceiling, we look down past the PANOPTICON tower into the large one roomed prison. The guard tower, cells, eating area, pool are all visible. This is our stage. The whole room is gray concrete or metal, utilitarian, well used, timeless. Robovac are scrubbing the walls, whirring.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 2</p>
                <p>Floor level view looking up at the guard tower. It dominates the room. Shielded, inaccessible. The glass is mirrored and swirling hypnotically. There are shiny glass circles arranged around the base at different heights. There is no visible way in. Silent but menacing. There is a low rumble, maybe.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 3</p>
                <p>We are looking down the line of the cells. Each cell has a circle in front of it and they are getting smaller as they recede into the distance.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 4</p>
                <p>We see the Tali, a technological looking pendant hanging on a pedestal in the center of the communal space, still moving slightly as if just hung up.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 5</p>
                <p>Looking into a sparse prison cell. There are no doors or bars. <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span>, a reddish orange beast in a prison jumpsuit is snoring under a blanket.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 6</p>
                <p>We see <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span>, a small humanoid with pink skin and face markings, also in a prison jumpsuit, half sitting/half lying in the corner under an interface module panel of buttons and switches by the only door-like opening in the room. A cot and blanket are there too. It looks like she passed out from fatigue despite trying to stay awake.</p>
                <p class="mt-2">A KLAXON goes off, filling the prison with sound.</p>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs mt-1">SFX: WREET! WREET!</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- PAGE 2 -->
          <div class="border-l-2 border-p-accent/30 pl-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-sm tracking-widest text-p-accent mb-6">PAGE 2 — BODY COUNT</h3>

            <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-p-text text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 1</p>
                <p>Close up. <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span> opens one eye.</p>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs mt-1">SFX: WREET! WREET!</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 2</p>
                <p>Wide panel. We see the line of cells with the different inmates waking and moving towards the circles arranged in front of each cell. We see some armbands and they have small yellow lights on them.</p>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs mt-1">SFX: WREET! WREET!</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 3</p>
                <p>Looking down the line of 8 inmates. Rubbing their eyes awake. Yawning, stretching, scratching their balls, pulling on jumpsuits. This is a scene they relive everyday. We see <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span> in the distance, just starting to stand, late.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 4</p>
                <p>Close up of <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span>. She looks like she is unsure if she will make it to her circle.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 5</p>
                <p>Trick is approaching the circle in front of Cell 6. <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> is in front of Cell 7. <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span>'s spot is Cell 5. We see Arcin approaching her spot slowly. Her arm band is yellow. The circle to the far left, Cell 8, is empty.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-text font-ui text-xs">TRICK:</span> Pillory's gone?!?</p>
                  <p><span class="text-p-red font-ui text-xs">MARUK:</span> Well, her cell is empty and the Tali is hanging on the Ped, so yeah. I think she's vented.</p>
                  <p><span class="text-p-text font-ui text-xs">TRICK:</span> Fu'uck.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 6</p>
                <p>Shot over Trick's and <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span>'s shoulders looking towards the Pedestal. We see the Tali hanging. <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span> is just passing through the frame. Her arm band is still yellow. Trick's and Maruk's armbands ping from yellow to green as they step on the circles. A scan begins to pass over their bodies.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-text font-ui text-xs">TRICK:</span> <em>She shouldn't have talked about…you know.</em></p>
                  <p><span class="text-p-red font-ui text-xs">MARUK:</span> Well that's for fucking sure.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 7</p>
                <p>Medium shot of <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> flexing his chest, bathed in the continuing body scan. We see Trick and <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span> to his left, maybe Schlager, a blue beast with an eye patch, armband green, looking on with dawning curiosity/anger.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-red font-ui text-xs">MARUK:</span> I'm taking the Veil, fuckers. Pillory's vented and I'm fucking next so fucking fuck off!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- PAGE 3 -->
          <div class="border-l-2 border-p-accent/30 pl-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-sm tracking-widest text-p-accent mb-6">PAGE 3</h3>

            <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-p-text text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 1</p>
                <p>Schlager steps one foot off his circle towards <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> and his armband turns yellow.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-accent font-ui text-xs">SCHLAGER:</span> The Hells, Maruk!?</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 2</p>
                <p>Schlager is fully off his circle and his armband pings red. He is approaching the Tali along with <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span>, whose arm band also pings red. <span class="text-[#8c78cc]">Donkey</span>, a skinny, worried looking bird-like alien with a robotic leg is seen behind them, looking scared. <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span> is getting scanned by a beam of light. The Klaxon sounds off again.</p>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs mt-1">SFX: WREET! WREET!</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-[#8c78cc] font-ui text-xs">DONKEY:</span> At least wait for the scan to finish!</p>
                  <p><span class="text-p-red font-ui text-xs">MARUK:</span> I'll hold The Veil, you slimy fucks! Go vent!</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 3</p>
                <p>Schlager and <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> are both lunging for the Tali. Maruk is just ahead. First mover's advantage. Their circle scans in the background are failing.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-red font-ui text-xs">MARUK:</span> Aurgh!</p>
                  <p><span class="text-p-accent font-ui text-xs">SCHLAGER:</span> Wrauwrrr!</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 4</p>
                <p><span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> down punches Schlager and grasps the Tali simultaneously.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 5</p>
                <p><span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> holds the Tali high, Schlager is in the background, shaking off the blow.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-red font-ui text-xs">MARUK:</span> Haha! I hold The Veil!</p>
                </div>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs mt-1">SFX: WREET! WREET!</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 6</p>
                <p>Shot of more of the inmates getting scanned. <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> running back to the line, armband pings yellow as he is approaching his circle. He is headed for the top spot, Cell 8.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- PAGE 4 -->
          <div class="border-l-2 border-p-accent/30 pl-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-sm tracking-widest text-p-accent mb-6">PAGE 4</h3>

            <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-p-text text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 1</p>
                <p>Darrow, a humanoid man with a full beard throws his arms up.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-text font-ui text-xs">DARROW:</span> Standing on this fucking circle for a few span every morning is the only thing you have to do all day and you fucking that up! C'mon!</p>
                </div>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs mt-1">SFX: WREET! WREET!</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 2</p>
                <p>We see down the line of inmates. Darrow peering at the newly reformed line. Schlager stepping on, pinging green, getting scanned. <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> is doubled over catching his breath on the top spot, his scan finishing.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-accent font-ui text-xs">SCHLAGER:</span> If I wasn't torn up, Maruk, I'd challenge.</p>
                  <p><span class="text-p-red font-ui text-xs">MARUK:</span> Keep saying you're torn up, but not how, Schlager so shut it.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 3</p>
                <p>Schlager is looking up towards the tower, fearful, eye wide, hand to the patch covering the other eye.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-accent font-ui text-xs">SCHLAGER:</span> Don' zackly remember's all.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 4</p>
                <p>Shot of the Panopticon tower windows, shiny, reflective, we cannot see who is behind them or if there even is anyone watching. A robovac is cleaning the walls.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p class="italic text-p-dim"><span class="text-p-accent font-ui text-xs">SCHLAGER</span> <span class="text-p-dim text-xs">(mumbling):</span> Mind's fuzzy around that. Just woke with a fucked eye.</p>
                </div>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs mt-1">SFX: WREET! WRE-</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 5</p>
                <p>Wide shot of the line of inmates, all armbands are green. <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> is putting the Tali around his neck. <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span> slumped. <span class="text-[#8c78cc]">Donkey</span> fidgeting with his feather fingers nervously.</p>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs mt-1">SFX: DOM DOM DOM</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 6</p>
                <p>Same shot of inmates but from the back. We see the new inmate cubicle/pod with constantly swirling glass doors across the large room. The doors have just cracked open and steam is escaping.</p>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs mt-1">SFX: DOM DOM DOM</p>
                <p class="font-display text-p-teal text-xs">SFX: Pshhhh</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- PAGE 5 -->
          <div class="border-l-2 border-p-accent/30 pl-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-sm tracking-widest text-p-accent mb-6">PAGE 5</h3>

            <div class="space-y-6 font-body text-p-text text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 1</p>
                <p>The door is open, full of steam and we see the silhouette of a humanoid figure with what looks like a big glove on one arm. We see the glow of his armband with the indicator light red.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 2</p>
                <p>Zoom in and we see a new inmate emerge from the steam. This is <span class="text-[#d4aa30]">Itsahk</span>, alien, yellow, hairless with large, kind eyes. He is standing tall and straight and has a slight smile on his lips.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 3</p>
                <p>Down the line of all the inmates as <span class="text-[#d4aa30]">Itsahk</span> approaches.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-[#d966d6] font-ui text-xs">ARCIN:</span> Stand on the circle. There.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 4</p>
                <p>Front view of <span class="text-[#d4aa30]">Itsahk</span> getting in line, looking forward, armband pinging green. <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span> to his left and <span class="text-[#d966d6]">Arcin</span> to his right, both looking across him. Arcin finally seems to have perked up.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-red font-ui text-xs">MARUK:</span> What the fuck is he smiling about?</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 5</p>
                <p><span class="text-[#d4aa30]">Itsahk</span> is still looking forward, maybe eyes turned slightly towards <span class="text-p-red">Maruk</span>. He takes Maruk's old spot, armband yellow.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-[#d4aa30] font-ui text-xs">ITSAHK:</span> Hmm?</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <p class="font-ui text-p-dim text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">PANEL 6</p>
                <p>Schlager speaking to PIKE. PIKE looking confused, maybe scratching his chin.</p>
                <div class="mt-2 pl-4 border-l border-p-dim/30">
                  <p><span class="text-p-accent font-ui text-xs">SCHLAGER:</span> When's the last time we got a new one? Anybody remember?</p>
                  <p><span class="text-p-text font-ui text-xs">PIKE:</span> Been a while. Can't even…hnhh.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Bottom nav -->
        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-p-unlock/10 flex items-center justify-between">
          <a href="/unlocked/002" class="font-ui text-p-unlock/60 text-xs tracking-widest hover:text-p-unlock transition-all">← FILE 002</a>
          <a href="/unlocked/004" class="font-ui text-p-unlock/60 text-xs tracking-widest hover:text-p-unlock transition-all">FILE 004 →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>

<script>
  const isComplete = localStorage.getItem('panopticon_intake_complete') === 'true';
  if (isComplete) {
    document.getElementById('access-denied')?.classList.add('hidden');
    document.getElementById('access-granted')?.classList.remove('hidden');
  }
</script>
